								<!-- bodytext -->
				<div class="dablink">This article is about Mon language, spoken in southeastern Burma and western Thailand; <b>Peguan</b> is redirected here.  For the northeastern Thai, northwestern Lao, and northern Vietnamese language of the Hmong, see <a href="/wiki/Hmong_language" title="Hmong language">Hmong language</a>.</div>
