k (<span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA">/kaˀ/</span>)</td>
<td><big><span style="font-family:Padauk, Parabaik, Myanmar3, Myanmar2, Myanmar1, MyMyanmar, Thanlwin, Masterpiece Uni Sans">ခ</span></big><br />
