<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Mon_language&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10" title="Edit section: Classifiers">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Classifiers">Classifiers</span></h3>
<p>Like many other Southeast Asian languages, Mon has <a href="/wiki/Classifier_(linguistics)" title="Classifier (linguistics)">classifiers</a> which are used when a noun appears with a numeral. The choice of classifier depends on the semantics of the noun involved.</p>
