<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Mon_language&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11" title="Edit section: Sentences">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Sentences">Sentences</span></h2>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Mon_language&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12" title="Edit section: Affirmative sentences">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Affirmative_sentences">Affirmative sentences</span></h3>
<p>The ordinary word order for sentences in Mon is Subject-Verb-Object, as in the following examples</p>
<table class="wikitable">
<tr>
